This project focused on understanding **consumer behavior in the stationery category on digital platforms** for **Hồng Hà Stationery**. The goal was to uncover how different customer groups discover, evaluate, and purchase stationery online, then translate those findings into strategic direction for the brand’s digital growth. The work combined market landscape analysis, category behavior, customer segmentation, and channel insight to help Hồng Hà compete more effectively in an increasingly platform-driven market.
